snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin': CG5 Edition (OUT NOW)
snippet.description:
Download the free Friday Night Funkin' game mod now!
▶ https://gamebanana.com/gamefiles/14966
Download Friday Night Funkin'!

Music by CG5
Artist: elikapika ▶ https://twitter.com/eleekapika
Charter: SandPlanet ▶ https://twitter.com/SandPlanetNG
Programmer: DoDo ▶ https://twitter.com/_DoDo_1334
Executive Production by Axie ▶ https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuusrNG27Cy5a_2cG41gnXg

Stream the original songs!
Spotify ▶ https://spoti.fi/375ek3t
Apple Music ▶ https://apple.co/3bfXoZo

You've finally made it to the big leagues of the music world, but of course there's a twist. To prove your worth, you have to beat the one and only CG5 in a battle of lyrical wits. Show him what you got!

This mod includes:
• CG5 as Daddy Dearest
• Three new songs in every difficulty
• New background assets
• OR3O as GF and Tutorial remix ▶ https://youtube.com/channel/UCTAyRNwgMv_vvM8Z9UvKKEg
• Title Screen remix
